<p><span>3.依照问题顺序提出改进方式</span></p>
<p><span>4.以加强语气强调改进的决心</span></p>
<p><span>5.表达想要收到回信的迫切</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200929/b0dbc3971d424cef93a57a3b2ca7258e.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span><strong><span>标准的申诉信模板（仅供参考）</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><span>一、</span>售卖<strong>假冒商品</strong>移除销售权限</span></p>
<p><span>Dear Amazon seller support,</span><span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
